SAF-K8S Split License

This project uses a split licensing structure, finalized at the 2026-05-18
Secure Agentic Framework (SAF) meeting:

1. Specification License
   All specification content — including the security control catalog, framework
   crosswalks, knowledge area structure, domain taxonomy (the YAML source files and
   the generated markdown pages), and the accompanying written documentation, published
   under the `SAF-K8S-*` identifiers — is licensed under the Community Specification
   License 1.0 (CSL 1.0).

   License file: LICENSE-CSL-1.0.md
   Working Group scope (patent-commitment bounds): SCOPE.md

2. Code License
   All code, including the catalog generation tooling (generate_markdown.py), is
   licensed under the Apache License, Version 2.0. The Community Specification License
   is, by its own terms, not intended for source code.

   Full license text: https://www.apache.org/licenses/LICENSE-2.0
   License file: LICENSE-APACHE-2.0

The full text of each license is provided in the respective files within this repository.
